{"data":[{"date":"14:56 23/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Suarez khoe s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam con","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/tien-dao-suarez-khoe-sap-co-them-con.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sofia Balbi cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u to ra nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi mang thai \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 ba.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Suarez \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf bi\u1ec3n sau World Cup 2018. Uruguay b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft b\u1edfi Ph\u00e1p - \u0111\u1ed9i sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Barca khoe \u1ea3nh qu\u1ef3 g\u1ed1i, \u00f4m v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 h\u00f4n l\u00ean b\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4. H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh cho th\u1ea5y v\u00f2ng ba c\u1ee7a Sofia Balbi kh\u00e1 to. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh thai nhi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Suarez v\u00e0 Sofia Balbi c\u00f3 hai con m\u1ed9t trai m\u1ed9t g\u00e1i l\u00e0 Delfina v\u00e0 Benjamin.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/cc-6175-1532223158.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay g\u1eb7p Arab Saudi \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Suarez th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tin vui v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c v\u1ee3 mang b\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 ba. Sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 23, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch chia vui v\u1edbi c\u00e1c fan. Anh chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \"H\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Uruguay v\u1edbi 100 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Vui m\u1eebng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0a con th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eafp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00ec s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn, \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 ba s\u1eafp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Barca \"\u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbp\" b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf CLB x\u1ee9 Catalonia l\u00e0 Messi - ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n qu\u00fd t\u1eed th\u1ee9 ba trong n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo b\u1eadn d\u1ef1 World Cup, Suarez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n \u1edf Barca, kh\u00f4ng tham gia c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Uruguay t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau Cup T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Sevilla tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi La Liga kh\u1edfi tranh.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4529","checkdouble":"191835"},{"date":"15:17 23/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea mang c\u1ea3 Italia sang x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/tan-hlv-chelsea-mang-ca-italia-sang-xu-so-suong-mu.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4528","checkdouble":"191837"},{"date":"14:28 23/07","title":"Juventus nh\u1eafm b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU thay Pjanic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/juventus-nham-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu-thay-pjanic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mua Paul Pogba trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Miralem Pjanic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Miralem Pjanic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus. Ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i ghi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p t\u1edbi 15 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Juventus-mua-Paul-Pogba-thay-Pjanic-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Juventus mua Paul Pogba thay Pjanic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Juventus mua Paul Pogba thay Pjanic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>PSG v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pjanic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/messi-muon-barca-mua-eriksen-hoac-pjanic-thay-vi-griezmann-180-187644.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Adrien Rabiot \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pjanic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 PSG v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mua Pogba thay Pjanic</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus mua Paul Pogba trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Miralem Pjanic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/juventus-nham-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu-thay-pjanic.jpg\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba\" alt=\"Mourinho phat bieu ve Pogba\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus mua Pogba trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Pjanic ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Pogba, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Juventus s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 60 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Pjanic, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u00f9 th\u00eam 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3. Theo Mirror, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ronaldo \u1edf Serie A, n\u1ebfu Pogba quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ra \u0111i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Pogba n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4527","checkdouble":"191831"},{"date":"15:01 23/07","title":"Bayern b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 mua Vidal cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/5/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mua Vidal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League sau v\u00e0i n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng, Inter Milan quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 Radja Nainggolan v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 38 tri\u1ec7u Euro bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 Davide Santon v\u00e0 Nicolo Zaniolo t\u1edbi AS Roma theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Nerazzurri \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Sime Vrsaljko c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/5/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nInter t\u1eebng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Vidal song \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu th\u1ed1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Nh\u1eefng Thiago Alcantara, Javi Martinez, Leon Goretzka, Sebastian Rudy, Corentin Tolisso v\u00e0 Renato Sanches \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Vidal ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y song kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e3i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria mu\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Inter 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u00e0i Inter, h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m AC Milan c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang kh\u00e1t ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Vidal. Cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile l\u00ean \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Uli Hoeness c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Serie A tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lazio-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-alex-iwobi-172-191833.html\">Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-nham-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu-thay-pjanic-172-191831.html\">Juventus nh\u1eafm b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU thay Pjanic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo-172-191736.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4526","checkdouble":"191832"},{"date":"17:14 23/07","title":"Ibra g\u1ea5y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m... T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/4/ibra-gay-soc-voi-tuyen-bo-muon-lam-tong-thong-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9 trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIbra ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1981 \u0111ang h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp LA Galaxy h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ai nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic, nh\u01b0ng anh lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang ti\u1ebfc r\u1ebb v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp MLS trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. B\u1edfi n\u1ebfu g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, anh t\u1ef1 tin m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m&hellip; T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9 nh\u01b0 Donald Trump l\u00fac n\u00e0y. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u01b0? T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang l\u00e0m c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i LA Galaxy m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb 10 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea3 qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9\" title=\"Ibrahimovic trong mau ao LA Galaxy\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/ibra-gay-soc-voi-tuyen-bo-muon-lam-tong-thong-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Donald Trump \u01b0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m l\u1eafm. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 gia nh\u1eadp Nh\u00e0 tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Hi\u1ebfn ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 cha m\u1eb9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng sau 15 tr\u1eadn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o LA Galaxy, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 36 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n hu\u00eanh hoang v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n ng\u00f4ng cu\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1eebng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9, anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i quay l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3. V\u1ee5 thua c\u01b0\u1ee3c David Beckham trong tr\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, khi Ibra ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn SV\u0110 Wembley \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu-172-191638.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu-172-191638.html\">Ibra ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi M.U</span><br>\r\nSau khi y\u00ean \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i MLS, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Zlatan Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\">Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nZlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Pogba sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4525","checkdouble":"191844"},{"date":"16:04 23/07","title":"Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/15/them-mot-ngoi-sao-dem-hung-tin-toi-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</h2><h2>Real quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Khong-de-de-Real-Madrid-dua-Eden-Hazard-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mua Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Los Blancos c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2020, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chia tay s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Hazard c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Hazard t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Hazard b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mirror, Chelsea \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef Hazard b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid, ngay c\u1ea3 khi Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, n\u1ebfu The Blues ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Real \u00e9p gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u00ednh to\u00e1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Mirror, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 80 \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 12 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4524","checkdouble":"191840"},{"date":"16:27 23/07","title":"MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Bernabeu. D\u00f9 The Blues kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg\" title=\"MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Hazard k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues nh\u1eafm thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Martial, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge. Chelsea tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Bayern Munich, Real Madrid v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 r\u1eddi Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Anthony Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/martial-co-tiem-nang-tro-thanh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, song M.U c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Manchester Evening News, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester mu\u1ed1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Martial \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Mourinho d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft ra \u0111i, MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Manchester Evening News kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 <br>\r\nti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea hay Bayern s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4523","checkdouble":"191841"},{"date":"16:52 23/07","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Roma mua Petr Cech thay Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Roma b\u00e1n Alisson cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech.jpg\" title=\"Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Roma nh\u1eafm Petr Cech thay Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRoma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Olympico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Leno t\u1eeb Bundesliga, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Petr Cech b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda. Roma tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1982 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Cech l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Arsenal b\u00e1n Cech, Roma ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Petr Cech</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Roma chi ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, song h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Chelsea trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech</span> trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech.jpg\" title=\"Cech\" alt=\"Cech\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Roma v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f9ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i \u01b0u ti\u00ean tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Cech \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng \u1edf London, anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Petr Cech, Roma s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Mignolet c\u1ee7a Liverpool. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield sau khi The Kop \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4522","checkdouble":"191845"},{"date":"17:16 23/07","title":"Leicester ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/5/leicester-phu-phang-voi-gary-cahill.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</h2><h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Gary Cahill</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea t\u1eeb Bolton v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Blues. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/5/leicester-phu-phang-voi-gary-cahill.jpg\" title=\"Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cahill</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-san-sang-chia-tay-cahill-172-191493.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Gary Cahill </span>\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 15 \u0111\u1ebfn 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Cahill, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Jonny Evans t\u1eeb West Brom song Leicester v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Cahill trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hary Maguire c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Gary Cahill</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/cahill.PNG\" title=\"cahill\" alt=\"cahill\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Cahill</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m Cahill, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Leicester s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Harry Maguire \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng M.U chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb Leicester kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb Gary Cahill s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi b\u1edfi HLV Sarri v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. Hi\u1ec7n West Ham, Everton v\u00e0 Southampton l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Cahill.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4521","checkdouble":"191846"},{"date":"17:42 23/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 23/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-2307.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 23/07. </h2><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2307--hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2307  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2307  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>AC Mian c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGazzetta dello Sport tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 AC Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri nh\u1eafm thay Morata.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Leicester ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Courtois.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech-172-191845.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech-172-191845.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal</span><br>\r\n<span>Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mundo Deportivo, Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 50, 53 v\u00e0 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Anthony Martial cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nExpress Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Anthony Martial cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0 Chelsea hay Tottenham, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe mu\u1ed1n PSG mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL'Equipe \u0111\u01b0a tin, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi PSG k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi N'Golo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. The Blues s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ngay c\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/15/them-mot-ngoi-sao-dem-hung-tin-toi-cho-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\">Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh thay Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/David-Moyes-phat-bieu-ve-Jordan-Pickford-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"thu mon Pickford\" alt=\"thu mon Pickford\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Jordan Pickford v\u00e0 Jack Butland trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real. Trong s\u1ed1 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Blues c\u00f3 Butland cao h\u01a1n Pickford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea v\u1ee5 Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, song h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Mirror kh\u1eb3ngd \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4520","checkdouble":"191849"},{"date":"09:11 23/07","title":"Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a \"s\u00f3i gi\u00e0\" Monchi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/thu-mon-alisson-den-liverpool-dau-an-cua-soi-gia-monchi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn Monchi - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng sau m\u00e0n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3u Monchi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AS Roma v\u1eeba chia tay th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Liverpool. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1eeb Transfermarkt, AS Roma thu v\u1ec1 123.2 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, chi ra 101.45 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 12 t\u00e2n binh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a s\u00f3i gi\u00e0 Monchi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a s\u00f3i gi\u00e0 Monchi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Thu-mon-Alisson-den-Liverpool-Dau-an-cua-soi-gia-Monchi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool gi\u00fap AS Roma c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<br>\r\n7 trong 12 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a AS Roma h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 23 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng. Ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u1ea5y ngay phong c\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7y quen thu\u1ed9c g\u1eafn v\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Monchi, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Monchi c\u0169ng mang v\u1ec1 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi cho AS Roma v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ecf ra l\u00e0 87.95 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong khi thu v\u1ec1 108.25 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Monchi t\u1ea1i AS Roma, h\u00e3y so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi AC Milan. H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Rossoneri b\u1ed5 sung 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea3i chi l\u00e0 189.5 tri\u1ec7u euro, ch\u1ec9 thu v\u1ec1 23.7 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ai c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a AC Milan ra sao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a s\u00f3i gi\u00e0 Monchi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a s\u00f3i gi\u00e0 Monchi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Alisson-den-Liverpool-voi-muc-gia-ky-luc-Dau-an-cua-soi-gia-Monchi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Monchi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, AS Roma m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Monchi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua scudetto v\u1edbi Juventus nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t t\u1ea1i Champions League. \"B\u1ea7y s\u00f3i\" l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 34 n\u0103m, l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 v\u1edbi Barcelona hay Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Sevilla, AS Roma kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Monchi h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng, quay v\u00f2ng v\u1ed1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Monchi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, AS Roma chia tay hai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t l\u00e0 Alisson Becker v\u00e0 Radja Nainggolan. Tr\u00ean c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n, nh\u1eefng Romanista li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ra s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0i nghi v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Monchi n\u00f3i ri\u00eang, c\u1ee7a ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o AS Roma n\u00f3i chung. \u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ho\u00e0i nghi, Monchi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch: \"B\u00e1n Alisson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m, m\u00e0 cho nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1edbi\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Day thu mon Alisson den Liverpool, Monchi mang ve den 12 tan binh cho AS Roma he nay.\" title=\"\u0110\u1ea9y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool, Monchi mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn 12 t\u00e2n binh cho AS Roma h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/monchi-1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ea9y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool, Monchi mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn 12 t\u00e2n binh cho AS Roma h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111a s\u1ed1 lf nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 AS Roma chinh chi\u1ebfn m\u00f9a 2016-17 l\u00e0 27.2. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Monchi, \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a AS Roma gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 26.75. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 25.5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a AS Roma d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Monchi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi lo ng\u1ea1i AS Roma s\u1ebd suy s\u1ee5p khi b\u00e1n Mohamed Salah (Liverpool) v\u00e0 Antonio Rudiger (Chelsea). D\u00f9 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf Serie A c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome c\u00f3 sa s\u00fat nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd su\u00fdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n, gi\u00e0u kh\u00e1t khao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a s\u00f3i gi\u00e0 Monchi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a s\u00f3i gi\u00e0 Monchi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/monchi-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Monchi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i cho AS Roma.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu theo d\u00f5i b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i c\u1ee7a Monchi k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u1edf Sevilla, d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed7i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8, \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 1-2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra \u0111i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 Sevilla kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 suy s\u1ee5p sau khi m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf AS Roma c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hay th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Alisson v\u00e0 Nainggolan ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u1edf Sevilla, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta g\u1ecdi Monchi l\u00e0 \"s\u00f3i gi\u00e0\".<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool:</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-liverpool-danh-bai-chelsea-vu-alisson-172-191664.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-becker-giai-ma-tan-binh-liverpool-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191660.html\">Alisson Becker: Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool \u2013 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-ho-da-co-de-gea-cua-rieng-minh-172-191659.html\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson: H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh-172-191635.html\">V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4519","checkdouble":"191676"},{"date":"09:22 23/07","title":"V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a \"l\u00ean m\u00e2y\" sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/37644906_1127134190773741_5719358041116114944_n.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu mon Dang Van Lam\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/37644906_1127134190773741_5719358041116114944_n.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0 song nh\u1edd tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00ean sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra v\u1ec1 an to\u00e0n sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n &lsquo;bay l\u01b0\u1ee3n&rsquo; c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen d\u00e0nh cho anh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y L\u00e2m &quot;T\u00e2y&quot; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u Nga, \u00f4ng V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh&rsquo; B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;&#10;color:#222222\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4518","checkdouble":"191823"},{"date":"11:51 23/07","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/23/sau-vong-20-vleague-su-vo-doi-cua-ha-noi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Thanh H\u00f3a, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed9t tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 v\u1edbi n\u1eeda c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a V-League.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a h\u00fa v\u00eda tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson, Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng khi\u1ebfn cho kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng th\u00e0nh 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf 6 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/tuandeu-165-15322166038181671998768.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc FLC Thanh H\u00f3a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. S\u1ef1 tr\u1ed7i d\u1eady c\u1ee7a SLNA<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng khi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, tuy nhi\u00ean \u00edt ai ng\u1edd, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 8 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 Olaha tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1edf n\u00ean nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap SLNA s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 8 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League do CLB G\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1ed3ng T\u00e2m Long An thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2005. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y SLNA c\u00f2n \u0111ang m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH sau 20 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl-168-191757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl-168-191757.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 trong su\u1ed1t 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0. G\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t SLNA \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-3 chung cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Vinh sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2014.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL, d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" title=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura t\u1ea1m an to\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Matias Nicolas J.Gonzalez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura t\u1ea1m qua c\u01a1n b\u0129 c\u1ef1c. Sau hai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 leo l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. Duy tr\u00ec t\u1ed1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, c\u1eeda tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 14 tr\u00ean BXH. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u0110\u00f4 r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ecf ra h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng cho HLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u V\u0169 Quang B\u1ea3o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung g\u1ea5p g\u00e1p n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00fap C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u01a1n nguy k\u1ecbch? H\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y c\u1ea7n v\u1ef1c l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 ngu\u1ed9i l\u1ea1nh sau nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng sau s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i V-Leauge \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH sau vong 20 V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/BXH-vong-20-V-Leauge-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Highlight Thanh H\u00f3a 2-3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></h3>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/21/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4517","checkdouble":"191828"}]}